{"tid":1309981,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱喺街見到對中學生情侶喺度嘴嚟嘴去，我行埋去屌到佢地跪喺度喊","createTime":"2019-07-12T12:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T15:34:29.000Z","uid":150100,"like":6,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d5033827c79c15c83d28afcd58dcf6af4b3c7b30","tid":1309981,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:43:55.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n話說頭先放工諗住返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知喺巴土站度見到pair情侶喺度嘴嚟嘴去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手上揸住啲一睇就知係補習notes<br />\n於是我就行過去<br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男學生:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女學生：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我：喂，你地喺度做乜嘢？<br />\n個男學生鬆開嘴：kissy囉，未見過人kissy呀？<br />\n我：依家香港四面楚歌，十面埋伏，烏江自刎，身首異處，死無全屍，你地仲有閒情逸致喺度談兒女私情？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地同我跪喺度！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我依一喝滙聚咗依幾個月嚟嘅怒火，可以話驚天地泣鬼神，連隔離坐輪椅個阿婆都嚇到碌埋落地<br />\n咁嗰pair情侶就一嘢跪咗喺度，眼角亦都開始濕<br />\n<br />\n之後我一路屌，佢地就一路喊<br />\n屌到咁上下我見條女有啲悔意<br />\n就扶佢起身<br />\n安慰佢幾句就揚長而去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：樓主好波<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：樓主好型"},{"pid":"4f7dffcc8b365d0e034a0f467b7b776c39d7008e","tid":1309981,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a798c726dd8f0bf49c95b01dbaf6be1da4b4092b","tid":1309981,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:51:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3c566846ccbdccee4b117194148ac9c0b539df","tid":1309981,"uid":1381